==Before Starting the Event==
If you wish to challenge any difficulty above Easy this event, it is highly advised for players to read up the [[Rainy-Summer 2020 Event/Info|Info Tab]] first to understand about difficulty selection and ship-locking.

==Map Guide==
*This is a '''single fleet''' map
*CV(L/B), (F)BB(V) and Akitsumaru '''cannot be sortied''' to this area.
*The map is split into 2 parts. Phase 1 is to perform a Transport Operation at Node {{Event/Route|M|Red}}. Phase 2 is unlocking the 2nd part of the map and defeating the {{ShipLink|Abyssal Kuriles Princess|text=Abyssal Kuriles Princess}} at {{Event/Route|T|Red}}.
**The time spent on Phase 1 heavily depends on how much Transport Load-Off Equipment you can bring to the boss node {{Event/Route|M|Red}}. The [[Events/Mechanics|Mechanics Tab]] includes a list of TP Load-Off Equipment and how many points are reduced from the TP-bar.
**The Phase 2 boss is a standard high-armour Abyssal Princess that needs to be defeated in order to clear the map. She is accompanied by DDs and in Easy+, a Submarine Yo-class.

