===Phase 1: Transport Operation===
The Boss Node {{Event/Route|M|Red}} in this phase has some rare drops (DEs, Kamoi, Shinyou, Ooyodo). For admirals intending to farm for drops, not focusing too heavily on maximizing TP depletion per run in favor of damage and consistency can be an option.

'''1CL(T) 1AV 3DD''' or '''1CL(T) 4DD'''
*Routes {{Event/Route|A|blue|B|blue|C|blue|D|red|G|red|J|red|K|blue|L|green|M|red}}
*Speed is irrelevant
*No LoS requirement
*Nodes D and G are small submarine fleets
**Bring 2-3 OASW and Line Abreast
*Node J is a torpedo squadron
**Use [[Combat/Main/Vanguard_Formation| Vanguard formation]]
*Boss node M is a single submarine with up to 5 destroyers in Line Ahead formation
**Vanguard formation with 1+ OASW in the top half (first 2 ships of 5)
**Alternatively, Line Ahead formation with 1+ 3 slot OASW
**If shelling firepower is sufficient, Double Line is also viable for shelling accuracy and ASW damage

===Phase 2: Route Unlock & Defeating Abyssal Kuriles Princess===

====Unlocking Boss Route====
Obtain an A Rank or higher at Node {{Event/Route|F|Red}}. Only required for Hard.

====Depleting the HP Gauge====
Admirals have the option between a short route and a long route, which differ only by one submarine node.

<u>'''Long Route'''</u>

'''6XX'''<br />
Ex. 1CL 1CLT 1AV 3DD<br />
Ex. 1CL(T) 5DD<br />
Ex. 1CA 1CL(T) 4DD<br />
Ex. 1CA 1CLT 1CL 1AV 2DD
*Routes {{Event/Route|A|blue|B|blue|C|blue|E|blue|F|red|O|blue|R|red|Q|red|T|red}}
*LoS Cn2 >= 29 needed to guarantee routing to boss
*Nodes {{Event/Route|F|Red}} and {{Event/Route|R|Red}} are small submarine fleets
**Bring 1-2 OASW and Line Abreast or Vanguard
*Node {{Event/Route|Q|Red}} is a torpedo squadron
**Will sometimes contain a Light Cruiser He Class Kai on Hard
**Vanguard formation and position destroyers to take full advantage of evasion bonuses
*The boss node contains Abyssal Kuriles Princess and a submarine, along with several destroyers
**Use Vanguard formation (with 1+ OASW in the top half of the fleet), or Double Line formation to deal with the submarine
**Kuriles Princess is capable of damaging several ships alone (opening torpedo, shelling, closing torpedo, night battle DA), so it's better to have several ships capable of dealing high damage
